科技行业巨头敦促欧盟简化人工智能法规https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/news/tech-industry-giants-urge-eu-streamline-ai-regulations/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=tech-industry-giants-urge-eu-streamline-ai - 法规https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/news/tech-industry-giants-urge-eu-streamline-ai-regulations/#respondRyan Daws Thu, 19 Sep 2024 15:20:55 +0000 Artificial IntelligenceCompaniesDevelopmentEthics & SocietyLegislation & GovernmentMeta (Facebook)aiartificial intelligenceethicseueuropeeuropean uniongovernmentlawlegalregulationSociety https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/?p=16117 <p> Meta 率先发出了一封公开信，呼吁紧急改革欧盟的人工智能法规。这封信获得了爱立信、SAP 和 Spotify 等 50 多家知名公司的支持，并作为广告刊登在《金融时报》上。这些行业领导者的集体声音凸显了一个紧迫的问题：欧洲的官僚主义<a class="excerpt-read-more" href="https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/news/tech-industry-giants-urge-eu-streamline-ai-regulations/" title="ReadTech行业巨头敦促欧盟简化人工智能法规">……阅读更多 ”</a></p><p>后<a href="https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/news/tech-industry-giants-urge-eu-streamline-ai-regulations/">科技行业巨头敦促欧盟简化人工智能法规的消息</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com">《人工智能新闻》</a>上。</p> ; 
<p><a href="https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/news/metas-ai-strategy-building-for-tomorrow-not-immediate-profits/">Meta</a>率先发出了一封公开信，呼吁紧急改革欧盟的人工智能法规。这封信得到了 50 多家知名公司的支持，包括<a href="https://www.telecomstechnews.com/news/ai-ran-collaboration-advance-mobile-networks/">爱立信</a>、 <a href="https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/news/sap-taps-microsoft-generative-ai-technologies/">SAP</a>和 Spotify，并作为广告刊登在《 <a href="https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/news/ft-and-openai-ink-partnership-web-scraping-criticism/">金融时报》</a>上。</p><p>这些行业领导者的集体声音凸显了一个紧迫的问题：欧洲人工智能监管的官僚方式可能会抑制创新，并导致该地区落后于全球同行。</p><p>信中指出：“与其他地区相比，欧洲的竞争力和创新能力已经下降，而且由于监管决策不一致，欧洲现在面临着在人工智能时代进一步落后的风险。”信中描绘了欧洲大陆目前在人工智能竞赛中所处的严峻局面。</p><p>签署方强调了两个关键领域的关切。首先，他们指出“开放”模型的开发，这些模型可以免费使用、修改和进一步开发。这些模式因其“倍增效益并传播社会和经济机会”同时加强主权和控制的潜力而受到称赞。</p><p>其次，这封信强调了“多模式”模型的重要性，它集成了文本、图像和语音功能。签署者认为，从纯文本模型到多模态模型的飞跃类似于“只有一种感觉和拥有所有五种感觉之间的区别”。他们断言，这些先进模型可以显着提高生产力，推动科学研究，并为欧洲经济注入数千亿欧元。</p><p>然而，问题的关键在于监管环境。这封信表达了对人工智能模型训练数据使用的不确定性的失望，这种不确定性源于欧洲数据保护机构的干预。他们认为，这种模糊性可能会导致大型语言模型 (LLM) 缺乏关键的欧洲特定训练数据。</p><p>为了应对这些挑战，签署方呼吁“根据欧盟数据法规做出协调、一致、快速和明确的决定，使欧洲数据能够用于人工智能培训，造福欧洲人”。他们强调需要采取“果断行动”来释放欧洲的创造力、独创性和创业精神的潜力，他们认为这对于该地区的繁荣和技术领先地位至关重要。</p><p>该信函的副本如下： </p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" width="636" height="1024" src="https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/meta-eu-ai-regulation-letter-artificial-intelligence-european-union-politics-law-legal-636x1024.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-16118" srcset="https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/meta-eu-ai-regulation-letter-artificial-intelligence-european-union-politics-law-legal-636x1024.jpg 636w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/meta-eu-ai-regulation-letter-artificial-intelligence-european-union-politics-law-legal-186x300.jpg 186w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/meta-eu-ai-regulation-letter-artificial-intelligence-european-union-politics-law-legal-768x1236.jpg 768w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/meta-eu-ai-regulation-letter-artificial-intelligence-european-union-politics-law-legal-954x1536.jpg 954w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/meta-eu-ai-regulation-letter-artificial-intelligence-european-union-politics-law-legal-124x200.jpg 124w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/meta-eu-ai-regulation-letter-artificial-intelligence-european-union-politics-law-legal-177x285.jpg 177w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/meta-eu-ai-regulation-letter-artificial-intelligence-european-union-politics-law-legal-155x250.jpg 155w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/meta-eu-ai-regulation-letter-artificial-intelligence-european-union-politics-law-legal-62x100.jpg 62w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/meta-eu-ai-regulation-letter-artificial-intelligence-european-union-politics-law-legal-37x60.jpg 37w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/meta-eu-ai-regulation-letter-artificial-intelligence-european-union-politics-law-legal.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 636px) 100vw, 636px" /></figure><p>虽然这封信承认了消费者保护的重要性，但它也强调了监管机构必须达到微妙的平衡，以避免阻碍商业进步。欧盟委员会的监管方式经常因其过于严厉而受到批评，而行业领袖的最新呼吁加剧了人们对该地区人工智能领域全球竞争力日益增长的担忧。</p><p>欧洲政策制定者面临的压力正在迅速增加，他们需要<a href="https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/news/balancing-innovation-trust-experts-assess-eu-ai-act/">创造一个促进创新的监管环境</a>，同时保持<a href="https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/news/uk-signs-ai-safety-treaty-to-protect-human-rights-and-democracy/">适当的保障措施</a>。未来几个月，行业利益相关者和监管机构之间可能会加强对话，解决这些将塑造欧洲人工智能发展未来的复杂问题。</p><p> <em>（ <a href="https://unsplash.com/@stereophototyp?utm_content=creditCopyText&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=unsplash">萨拉·库菲斯</a>摄）</em></p><p><strong>另请参阅：</strong> <a href="https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/news/solarwinds-it-professionals-stronger-ai-regulation/"><strong>SolarWinds：IT 专业人士希望加强人工智能监管</strong></a></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><a href="https://www.ai-expo.net/"><img decoding="async" width="728" height="90" src="https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/ai-expo-world-728x-90-01.png" alt="" class="wp-image-11874" srcset="https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/ai-expo-world-728x-90-01.png 728w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/ai-expo-world-728x-90-01-300x37.png 300w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/ai-expo-world-728x-90-01-380x47.png 380w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/ai-expo-world-728x-90-01-350x43.png 350w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/ai-expo-world-728x-90-01-100x12.png 100w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/ai-expo-world-728x-90-01-60x7.png 60w" sizes="(max-width: 728px) 100vw, 728px" /></a></figure><p><strong>想向行业领导者了解更多关于人工智能和大数据的知识吗？</strong>查看在阿姆斯特丹、加利福尼亚州和伦敦举办的<a href="https://www.ai-expo.net/">人工智能与大数据博览会</a>。该综合活动与<a href="https://intelligentautomation-conference.com/northamerica/">智能自动化大会</a>、 <a href="https://www.blockchain-expo.com/">BlockX</a> 、<a href="https://digitaltransformation-week.com/">数字化转型周</a>以及<a href="https://www.cybersecuritycloudexpo.com/">网络安全与云博览会</a>等其他领先活动同期举行。</p><p><a href="https://techforge.pub/events/">在此</a>探索由 TechForge 提供支持的其他即将举行的企业技术活动和网络研讨会。</p><p>后<a href="https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/news/tech-industry-giants-urge-eu-streamline-ai-regulations/">科技行业巨头敦促欧盟简化人工智能法规的消息</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com">《人工智能新闻》</a>上。</p> ; https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/news/tech-industry-giants-urge-eu-streamline-ai-regulations/feed/ 0
